🤔 Analysis Questions & Answers
1. Who are our most valuable customers?

Top customers contributed the highest percentage of overall revenue. These customers showed repeat purchasing behavior and high order frequency.

2. What products sell best together?

Cross-selling analysis revealed that accessories and electronics products were commonly purchased together.

3. Which regions have highest sales?

The South region generated the highest revenue among all regions.

4. What are the seasonal trends?

Sales increased significantly during festive and holiday seasons, with December recording the highest sales.

5. How can we improve customer retention?

Customer retention can be improved through:

Loyalty reward programs
Personalized product recommendations
Seasonal discounts
Improved customer service
Cross-selling strategies
✅ Recommendations
Increase marketing in high-performing regions.
Focus inventory management on best-selling products.
Provide loyalty rewards for repeat customers.
Improve cross-selling opportunities.
Use seasonal sales trends for better forecasting.
🎯 Conclusion

This project successfully demonstrates advanced data manipulation and business analytics using Pandas.

The analysis provides valuable business insights related to customer behavior, regional sales performance, seasonal trends, and product demand. The project also highlights the importance of data-driven decision-making for improving revenue and customer retention.

